{"tid":2240451,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國國金證券和國聯證券資產重組終止","createTime":"2020-10-12T15:56:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T15:56:00.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"aaf52a087529aaa86956d3bec4beb680439f6987","tid":2240451,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T15:56:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554327-20201012.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554327-20201012.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=W9k3bdIekjUozLnTtmc2V3O0ZW31AiaZ%2BXmqixBX3cM%3D&h=043f5f33\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1554327-20201012.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=7d7aa80f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1554327-20201012.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n中國國金證券發布公告指，與國聯證券的資產重組終止，控股股東終止轉讓股份是因為交易相關方，未能就轉讓及合併方案的部分核心條款達成一致意見。<br />\n<br />\n公告又指，各方對終止今次交易無需承擔任何違約責任，不會影響公司的正常經營。<br />\n<br />\n國聯證券亦表示，公司決定終止籌劃今次重大資產重組事項，公司A股明日復牌。<br />\n<br />\n另外，國金證券A股明日亦將復牌。"}]}